<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Your Jastip Request is Created!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
      
      <p>Your jastip request has been successfully created. Here are the details:</p>
      
      <ul>
        <li>Product URL: {{productUrl}}</li>
        <li>Total Amount: IDR {{amount}}</li>
        <li>Order ID: {{orderId}}</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Please complete the payment to activate your request. Once payment is completed, travelers will be able to see and respond to your request.</p>

      <p>
        <a href="{{paymentUrl}}" class="button">Complete Payment</a>
      </p>

      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>Team Bagasi</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>Â© {{year}} Bagasi. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
